description: Looking for a ice cold sweet treat on a hot day? Carmen's Italian Ice is bringing you many to choose from! Their menu boasts delicious italian ice in a variety of flavors, as well as frozen custard, frozen yogurt, or a combination of italian ice and frozen custard/yogurt called a gelati! Their menu also features a host of hot and cold drinks like milkshakes, smoothies, coffee, tea, hot chocolate and more!
name: Carmen's Italian Ice
